Phone - oneplus 5 OS - OOS If anyone has an issue from being in a bootloop, 
go to your recovery (TWRP) Once you are in your Recovery, make sure it is 
decrypted (if a password is set, put in your phone passcode. If no prompt 
pops up, you're okay) Press "install" Substratum And press the recovery 
file. Install this and reboot your device No data should be lost and you 
will be out of the bootloop If this doesn't work, wipe the phone to factory 
settings. It will wipe ALL of the data on your device, but, you will have 
your phone back.
